snippet.title: Little Raiders: Robin's Revenge -- Launch Trailer [EUROPE]
snippet.description:
Download for FREE now!
App Store: http://bit.ly/VPDprD

Little Raiders: Robin's Revenge is a wonderful mixture of adventure, combat and buildings experience. Build your village, raise your army of Raiders, recruit unique heroes and equip them with legendary weapons!
